始終唔係正規交通工具，生命冇保障，隨時連保險都唔撚賠，咁就真係得不償失。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:09:11.000Z","msg":"你點收的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fe8cce375abc778c41ce5f15c008b52200f809","tid":1747291,"uid":323319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:09:19.000Z","msg":"你點知的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322964f5cbb72c2ee4cf3f7afc29cf745572f8b7","tid":1747291,"uid":310765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:09:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35c93462a78ca333b0622ae3e1eb15f583ad0b75","tid":1747291,"uid":41477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:09:34.000Z","msg":"老人院個班唔坐車點去投"},{"pid":"24d55478df43600726bc04b3ca6dcd908c8adcb3","tid":1747291,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:09:36.000Z","msg":"no sir"},{"pid":"0013e944fabc9533500f4c16b2557ceaf10adeb1","tid":1747291,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aee0c7143de9e7a0aff6a83b42f57b37a1db24d","tid":1747291,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:09:49.000Z","msg":"11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8yQUK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8yQUK2.png&h=727d0b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誠邀：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、民主派議員、及候選人<br />\n<br />\n等候時及面對<span style=\"color: red;\">白警</span>時唱<strong>《Sing Hallelujah To The Lord》</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港區 6:00pm 灣仔紅隧入口集合，大量兩層巴士接過紅隧，或自行行過紅隧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">致 撞區候選人，<br />\n必在 11月 24日 7:30am 前，在facebook發表，證明已為<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7－11pm</span></strong>申請不反通知書，否則只有零票。</span></span><br />\n撞區表 <a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fcrashes%2F1&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=0f068d63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1</a><br />\n<br />\n下期預告：12.1 民主歌聲撐林夕 圍繞理大走一圈 【行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747254</a>"},{"pid":"6a594bc31e731fcbb9af5a29147967255002c0fd","tid":1747291,"uid":28432,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"警務人員不誠實使用電腦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3bf293c1663c9dffb312f3e7b0f411c53a110f","tid":1747291,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:10:11.000Z","msg":"[深度數據分析] 你知道嗎？多你一票好多<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1746369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1746369</a>"},{"pid":"03416dd22c82c462e88594c810362d41eff16ae7","tid":1747291,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:10:15.000Z","msg":"你點燒的"},{"pid":"befc9a720e337fb55956421574f64feae637613e","tid":1747291,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33c766c92793dfe03e350f4f09132ab362a5b28","tid":1747291,"uid":244609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:11:11.000Z","msg":"你點知的"},{"pid":"d6948fd50770cf8e7f9e9362f523d6566c3940b9","tid":1747291,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:11:11.000Z","msg":"阿SIR你點知架"},{"pid":"491adf77397334df09ffbb6bb7a9ce1e0308dc27","tid":1747291,"uid":176027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:11:25.000Z","msg":"