,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:32:23.000Z","msg":"我收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca947a2cd730bc0d7d418484563b48bac3bdb52","tid":1747291,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9592c26e8cd3b69d1afa0fee88ceca4cb815dbb","tid":1747291,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:32:23.000Z","msg":"我收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:33:36.000Z","msg":"仲有冇人收到呀"},{"pid":"92e03c0cbae2e50fbf60fdb1866e33f6098ed159","tid":1747291,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:35:49.000Z","msg":"Sir"},{"pid":"3184675c8a4c4677f997043e6002f6dea1dca97d","tid":1747291,"uid":336224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4198db1d2654b33a6b0b15b58dc733a3b096f53","tid":1747291,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"「未FC」待FC<br />\nTG收到風，有消息指示威者針對攻擊去投票的賄選旅遊巴，聽日去投票坐賄選旅遊巴，隨晚會俾人燒，搞到屋企都返唔到。<br />\n我明白佢哋個邏輯，因為只要燒到一架旅遊巴，建制派就會損失一大堆賄選票。票站唔可能因為燒一架旅遊巴，即時將選舉押後7日，比盡只係延長時間，所以計落嗰班示威者有可能博得過呢一件事。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我係度呼籲明日不要座非正規旅遊巴前往票站去投票。<br />\n各位仔仔女女，唔該同曬你哋屋企人講，唔好懶，聽日去投票千祈唔好坐賄選旅遊巴。<br />\n<br />\n不論網上消息真假，其實坐上旅遊巴已經可能涉及收受選舉利益，廉政公署可以拉鳩你。<br />\n請坐正規公共交通工具，以免受暴力分子縱火，導致人命及財產損失。<br />\n<br />\n我依家開始擔心住喺老人院嘅公公婆婆。<br />\n唔該聽朝早啲孝子賢孫，個個去老人院探你嘅父母老人，共聚天倫，帶佢哋去飲茶，特別唔好畀佢哋坐老人院嘅賄選旅遊巴，以免無辜成為攻擊目標。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔知大家係咪都收到呢個訊息呢？？？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果係多人嘅話，政府真係要作出呼籲千祈唔好亂咁上旅遊巴。始終唔係正規交通工具，生命冇保障，隨時連保險都唔撚賠，咁就真係得不償失。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:37:02.000Z","msg":"又係你啊sir"},{"pid":"4db4331ecb6cc366e853f83f4109e5abdce5b6e4","tid":1747291,"uid":297453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:37:50.000Z","msg":"叔一燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88cd6dc038c61bb0871dcc6d6d4376c74ba0516","tid":1747291,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f578effd829bbabb5474a89021fd18c27121a88f","tid":1747291,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30920920ea60eb668dff3fb4a3be939cee72ea88","tid":1747291,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41677fb7470954483df711e047657378d425364d","tid":1747291,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5b0cacef881c82f156fd97cfefa8f08dc5a464","tid":1747291,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc4926c7c336c38abc12f1e3fd94ec08b4350ad","tid":1747291,"uid":302019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"Thank you, Sir! <img src=\"/as